BEGIN_PGML
Check if the given number is a solution to the given equation.

Is [`[$proposed_solution]`] a solution to [`[$left]=[$right]\text{?}`]

>> [@DataTable(
  [
    [PGML('[`[$left->TeX]`]'),
     PGML('[`=`]'),
     PGML('[`[$right->TeX]`]'),
    ],
    [PGML('[_]{$lefteval}{3}'),
     PGML('[`\wonder{=}`]'),
     PGML('[`[$righteval->TeX]`]'),
    ],
  ],
      align => 'rcl',
      valign => 'middle',);@]* <<

[_]{$dropdown}{5}

END_PGML

